Package cellularAutomata.cellState.model

Class Summary
CellState Holds the state for a cell in a cellular automaton.
CellStateFactory Creates flyweights for the CellState values.
ComplexState A cell state for a cellular automaton with complex numbers as states.
ComplexValuedVectorState A vector state of any length with any Complex values, represented as an array of Complex numbers.
IntegerCellState A cell state for a cellular automaton with values 0 through N-1.
IntegerVectorState A vector state of any length with any integer values, represented as an array of integers.
LatticeGasState State for hexagonal lattice gas automatons.
ObjectState A cell state for a cellular automaton with arbitrary objects as states.
RealValuedState A cell state for a cellular automaton with complex numbers as states.
RealValuedVectorState A vector state of any length with any double values, represented as an array of doubles.
